<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> bevor. <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        Zesel, als du uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hast von deinr kind
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu
                        macht du selb wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>, daz wir der sache in
                                <expan>sunderh<ex>eit</ex></expan> niht zu
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und als die sache mit recht für uns
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist und du und deine
                                <expan>kind<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> sein, so <expan>gunne<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>yegl<ex>ich</ex></expan> teil seins
                            <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>, wol <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> umb
                        gelimpfes <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir deine <expan>kind<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dein<ex>en</ex></expan> brief hörn <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>;
                        die <expan>spreche<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie söliche gebott vormals von dir
                        niht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und sie <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan>, dir
                        selb <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>.
                        Und als du <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> geleyts
                            <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hast, da ist
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> form und <expan>gewonh<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        niht, daz wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schribne</expan> geleyt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo Jacobi <expan>Grola<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri</expan>
<expan>civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>assump<ex>ci</ex><hi rend="sup">o<ex>n</ex>is</hi></expan> Marie
                                <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is</expan>.</ab>
</div>
